ks-station-event-nightshift-start-announcement = Attention! To reduce power consumption and relieve agitation of outside fauna, all of the lights aboard the station have been dimmed for the night.
ks-station-event-nightshift-end-announcement = Attention! As it is now day time, all of the lights aboard the station have been restored to their former brightness.

ks-station-event-nightshift-totalalert-start-announcement = Attention! Attention! Attention! The station is now in a state of total war. Prepare for the worst.
ks-station-event-nightshift-totalalert-end-announcement = Attention! The station is no longer in a state of total war.
